---
import Layout from "../layout/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Cancellation and Refund Policy | Neurotechh"
  description="Cancellation and Refund Policy for Neurotechh - Learn about our policies regarding cancellations and refunds."
  imgurl="https://neurotechh.xyz/seo.png"
>
  <section class="min-h-[80vh] w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 mt-[12vh]">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-incognito font-semibold text-brandred mb-8">
      Cancellation and Refund Policy
    </h1>
    
    <article class="prose prose-lg prose-invert prose-headings:text-brandred prose-headings:font-incognito prose-headings:font-semibold prose-p:text-text/80 prose-a:text-brandpink hover:prose-a:text-brandred prose-strong:text-brandred">
      <p class="text-lg">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</p>

      <h2>1. Cancellation Policy</h2>
      <p>
        You may cancel your participation in our programs or services according to the following guidelines:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Program cancellations must be made at least 7 days before the start date</li>
        <li>Workshop cancellations must be made at least 48 hours before the scheduled time</li>
        <li>Event cancellations must be made at least 14 days before the event date</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>2. Refund Policy</h2>
      <p>Our refund policy is as follows:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Full refund: Cancellation made 14+ days before the start date</li>
        <li>50% refund: Cancellation made 7-13 days before the start date</li>
        <li>No refund: Cancellation made less than 7 days before the start date</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. Refund Process</h2>
      <p>
        Refunds will be processed within 7-10 business days after the cancellation request is approved. The refund will be issued to the original payment method used for the purchase.
      </p>

      <h2>4. Special Circumstances</h2>
      <p>
        We understand that unexpected situations may arise. In case of medical emergencies or other exceptional circumstances, please contact us directly to discuss your situation.
      </p>

      <h2>5. Contact Information</h2>
      <p>
        For cancellation requests or questions about our refund policy, please contact us at:
        <br />
        <a href="mailto:contact@neurotechh.xyz">contact@neurotechh.xyz</a>
      </p>
    </article>
  </section>
</Layout> 